tweet: Untuk membantu kemudahan masyarakat di Masamba ,Telkomsel menghadirkan layanan bebas telpon gratis 50 menit dan 250 sms gratis ke semua operator, mulai tanggal 17 – 23 Juli 2020. Layanan tersebut dapat di akses melalui UMB *888*20# atau SMS dengan mengetik LUWU dan kirim ke 8999.
english: To help ease the people in Masamba, Telkomsel free service brings free calls 50 minutes and 250 free SMS to all operators, starting on 17 to 23 July 2020. The service can be accessed via UMB * 888 * 20 # or SMS by typing LUWU and send to 8999.

english: Now, people can enjoy the District of Masamba has returned to normal service access Telkomsel thoroughly to support the daily activities as usual.
